# Customer Journey Map Visual Representation

## Overview

Create a visual representation of the customer journey, including stages, touchpoints, emotions, and behaviors. Use tools like Miro or Signavio to create the visual representation.

## Output

* A customer journey map visual representation in a file named 'customer_journey_map.pdf' or 'customer_journey_map.png'
table
| Stage | Touchpoint | Emotion | Behavior |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Awareness | Social media ad | Curiosity | Clicks on ad |
| Consideration | Website visit | Interest | Reads product description |
| Purchase | Online purchase | Satisfaction | Makes purchase |

